{"tid":1740191,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"請放心，人權法一定過","createTime":"2019-11-20T00:50:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-20T12:25:14.000Z","uid":91648,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"12f6b998e9fd55de97abba7a53cc0c68694657c2","tid":1740191,"uid":91648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T00:50:33.000Z","msg":"對美國嚟講，香港具有地理戰略價值，美國一日影響到香港，就等如將戰線覆蓋到中國門口。中國一日尚未完全成為強國，一日都唔可以完全放棄香港。<br />\n<br />\n有人話美國會因為貿易戰談判而唔簽人權法，呢個不可能。香港嘅地理位置太重要，何況美國已經收緊稅，唔怕要多樣。<br />\n<br />\n情況就係黑社會係你間舖收緊陀地費，然後係出面擺咁盤桔，最重要係冇人俾呢個黑社會更惡。<br />\n<br />\n所以香港人，可以爭取，但不必驚慌。"},{"pid":"528ab5365ab7815f5eba0c7a3b581c185aaa746a","tid":1740191,"uid":249263,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T00:51:15.000Z","msg":"法案在參議院通過咗，大家快啲去多謝議員啦！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1740143\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1740143</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n幫推<br />\n<br />\nTwitter組24小時keep住更新<br />\n幫手retweet<br />\n㩒入👉<a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=qnfk3FWFLoR313jZLhvcNvilxGv0e2UEk%2F7kpEYl8nk%3D&h=dd309cbd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a><br />\n然後打 /task 攞任務"},{"pid":"4025ef16fb47693a9ccdd8cf81bd29f3d85d586f","tid":1740191,"uid":327414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T01:03:11.000Z","msg":"是不是現在只要Trump簽就得啦？"},{"pid":"ba3e45a66ec55d73e56febb7831151941c062bab","tid":1740191,"uid":91648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4025ef16fb47693a9ccdd8cf81bd29f3d85d586f","tid":1740191,"uid":327414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T01:03:11.000Z","msg":"是不是現在只要Trump簽就得啦？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T12:11:45.000Z","msg":"梗係。 佢冇得唔簽"},{"pid":"24586947089754f24825b86a91130db5caa2c007","tid":1740191,"uid":101345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T12:12:06.000Z","msg":"平反! 埋土投降既手足唔係懦弱, 而係負責